Type: Package
Title: FIREVAT, FInding REliable Variants without ArTifacts
Description: FIREVAT is a variant filtering tool for cancer sequencing data, 
    which uses mutational signatures to identify sequencing artifacts and 
    low-quality variants.
Version: 0.1.5
Authors: Andy Jinseok Lee, Hyunbin Kim
Maintainer: Andy Jinseok Lee <jinseok.lee@ncc.re.kr>, Hyunbin Kim <khb7840@ncc.re.kr>
